Package semanticMarkup.know.lib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CSVCorpus
    A CSVCorpus creates an ICorpus from a CSV file
    CSVGlossary
    A CSVGlossary creates an IGlossary from a CSV file; expected CSV file format: word;category
    GlossaryOrganStateKnowledgeBase
    GlossaryOrganStateKnowledgeBase creates an IOrganStateKnowledgeBase using an IGlossary
    LearnedCharacterKnowledgeBase
    LearnedCharacterKnowledgeBase poses an ICharacterKnowledgeBase by making use of learned terminology by an ITerminologyLearner and an IGlossary
    LearnedOrganStateKnowledgeBase
    LearnedOrganStateKnowledgeBase creates an IOrganStateKnowledgeBase relying on learned terminology
    LearnedPOSKnowledgeBase
    LearnedPOSKnowledgeBase poses an IPOSKnowledgeBase by relying on learned part of speech and using a fall back knowledgebase such as WordNetPOSKnowledgeBase
    WordNetPOSKnowledgeBase
    WordNetPOSKnowledgeBase poses an IPOSKnowledgeBase by relying on WordNet
